  "instructions": [
    "In a large bento box, combine baby new potatoes, halal beef broth, soy sauce, sugar, garlic, and ginger.",
    "Bring the braise to a boil over high heat, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "While the braise is cooking, mix gochujang and sesame oil in a small bowl.",
    "Add the gochujang mixture to the braise and stir to combine.",
    "Simmer the braise for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Garnish with green onions and sesame seeds.",
    "Serve the braise hot in the bento box.",
    "Enjoy!",
    "Let the braise rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "This will help the flavors to meld together."
